Name:
*  Yuliya Chermoshanskaya RUS disqualified for an anti-doping rule violation according to IOC Disciplinary Commissions desicion of August 14 2016. 




Women's 200 m - Athletics - Beijing 2008 Summer Olympics
Event Format:
     
     The 200 m race was run in marked lanes around the last curve and on the homestretch in the Olympic Stadium. Runners competed in preliminary heats, quarterfinals, semifinals and final. The best athletes from each heat (Q) and a number of "lucky losers" (q) advanced to the next level. The winner of the final was the Olympic gold medal winner. Event facts: Women's 200 m competition was held at the Beijing National Stadium and 46 athletes participated in the event.
